|CK0  Monkey is disruption and movement. It is less interested in a clean
|CK0  duel than in forcing the opponent out of shape.

|CK0  "leg sweep" and "grapple weapon" define the basic Monkey lesson:
|CK0  break footing, isolate the target, and take away control. Later,
|CK0  Monkey becomes one of the guild's main bridge styles, feeding into
|CK0  Snake with "coiled rise" or Tiger with "predator coil".

|CK0  Think of Monkey as:
|CK0    create chaos
|CK0    force openings
|CK0    hand the route into a deadlier style

|CK0  Common examples:
|CK0    leg sweep -> grapple weapon
|CK0    leg sweep -> coiled rise -> one-inch punch
|CK0    leg sweep -> predator coil -> roar

